{
  "text": "DNA was extracted according to the micro-extraction method described by [CITATION_1] . Tetra-primer ARMS-PCR was used to differentiate the alleles pvr2 1 , pvr2 2 , pvr2 3 and pvr2 + , as described by [CITATION_2] .",
